{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/gif-1.gif?t=1731332247\" /><br><br>Operation Marakudja is a fast-paced FPS where you can play both in single player mode and with other players online. Choose your character and go on a heated battle for the incredibly delicious fruits of Marakudja!<br><br>Each of the characters is armed with their own unique weapons. Hone your play style, find useful items and collect as many fruits as possible.<br><br>Explore a variety of environments, from deserts to lush jungles and futuristic landscapes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/title-1.png?t=1731332247\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/title-3.png?t=1731332247\" /><br><strong>Raid of Marakudja:</strong><br>Collect and steal Marakuji fruits from other players in this competitive mode where every loot counts. Destroy your opponents in exciting battles and try not to lose your loot to gain the upper hand over the other players.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/gif-2.gif?t=1731332247\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/title-4.png?t=1731332247\" /><br><strong>Marakudja Giant:</strong><br>Stand up to protect the Giant Marakudja and earn Marakudja every 5 seconds for as long as you hold it. Be vigilant, though, as your opponents will try to shoot you down to take control of the precious Giant Marakudja above your head.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/gif-3.gif?t=1731332247\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/title-5.png?t=1731332247\" /><br><strong>Balloons and Marakudja:</strong><br>This mode is all about survival. Protect your three balloons, which represent your lives, while collecting and stealing Marakudja from other players. If you lose your three balloons, you won't be able to reappear, so play smart to stay in the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/gif-4.gif?t=1731332247\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/title-2.png?t=1731332247\" /><br><br>Unlock a multitude of costumes as you progress with your character, gaining levels and unlocking new appearances for ultimate customization.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/image-1.png?t=1731332247\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/title-6.png?t=1731332247\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731332247","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/page.bg.jpg?t=1731332247","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731332247","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731332247","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2900970,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Follow me !</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img class=\"